binary-serializer provides header-only binary serialization.

Usage:
    find_package(binary-serializer CONFIG REQUIRED)
    target_link_libraries(main PRIVATE binary-serializer::binary-serializer)

Example:
    #include <binary-serializer/binary_serializer.hpp>
    bin::writer w;
    w.write(42);
    w.write(std::string("hello"));
    w.write(std::vector<int>{1, 2, 3});

    bin::reader r(w.data());
    auto x = r.read<int>();
    auto s = r.read<std::string>();
